  <brief_title>Telecare in Type 1 Diabetes (T1D) Patients Treated by Insulin Pump</brief_title>
  <official_title>Telecare in Adults With Type 1 Diabetes Mellitus Treated by Insulin Pump - A Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
