  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether Telecare can be used for efficient
      management of adults with Type 1 Diabetes Mellitus using insulin pump, in lieu of frequent
      clinic visits.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
